reviews.review_text:
This is some recording! extremely clean recording and crisp as hell.  fine separation of the band and they're all 'right there'.

as typical the year, terrific drums>space; beautiful jam into the Wheel.  O1>Dew!  terrific Boid Song in first set.
And some show!!! Brilliantly, excellently wonderful. Can't say more.
